
Real World Vue.js
----------------------

λ node --version
v12.16.2

1.- Intro to Real World Vue

Install CLI: npm i -g  @vue/cli
λ vue --version
@vue/cli 4.3.1

2.- Vue CLI 3 - Creating our Project
Create Proyect: vue create real-world-vue
               choose: Babel, router, Vuex, Linter / Formatter
               ESLint + Prettier
               Link on save
               In dedicated config files

Start Proyect: npm run serve

3. Optimizing your editor
-vuter: contiene vue-snipets 
     'vue', crea estructura

- eslint
- Prettier
- Copy Relative Path: 
     vue-mastering/Real World Vue.js/real-world-vue/src/views/Home.vue // @ is an alias to /src
     @/components/HelloWord.vue
- Vue VScode snipets
     vif: v-if=""
     von: @click="handler(arg, event)"
     vdata: estructura de data
     vprops:
     vimport
- theme: 
     FlatUI dark

